speaking. After a moments pause
Mr. Colden, I presume.
Yes, madam.
You wish to see my daughter?
I was anxious, madam, to see you. My
business
here chiefly lies with
you
, not
her
.
With me, sir? And pray, what have you to
propose to me.
I have nothing to solicit madam, but your
patient
attention. (I saw the rising vehemence
