At length, I stammered outSince it is the
lastthe last interviewif I were allowed
but one moment.
No, no, nowhat but needless torment to
herself and to you can follow? What do you
expect
from an interview?
I would see, for a moment, the face of one,
whomwhatever be
my
faults, and whatever be
hers
, I
love
.
Yes. You would profit, no doubt, by your
power over this infatuated girl. I know what
a rash proposal she has made you, and you
